             was indicted for <rs id="t17931204-55-off301" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17931204-55-off301" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17931204-55-off301" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17931204-55-cd302" type="crimeDate">26th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17931204-55-off301 t17931204-55-cd302"></join>, a silk handkerchief, value 6d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17931204-55-victim620" type="victimName">
                     Henry 
                     Croft
                  <interp inst="t17931204-55-victim620" type="surname" value="Croft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17931204-55-victim620" type="given" value="Henry"></interp>
